Life is returning to normal in Taiyuan, capital of Shanxi Province, with no reports of new Covid cases for nearly two months. With temperatures rising, more people now choose to go out at night to escape the daytime heat. The Zhongloujie walking street is one of the city's hot spots for shopping and tasting local delicacies. Local officials say the average daily customer flow has reached 30,000 in Zhongloujie walking street.